{"tid":589480,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"「輕小界高木」同佐伯同學係屋企做乜好呢？","createTime":"2018-03-12T01:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T02:18:20.000Z","uid":98507,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58c72f304c72335afd28ce68745881ac758b5087","tid":589480,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:26:39.000Z","msg":"《與佐伯同學住在同一屋簷下》<br />\n先前買左呢本嘅第一卷<br />\n哇屌你閃到眼盲<br />\n最緊要係閃得黎好睇呀嘛<br />\n網絡資源出到第二卷<br />\n岩岩睇完 正式宣布食用指數極高<br />\n<br />\n不過缺點就係離地得濟<br />\n咁撚岩同個索女住埋一齊 邊撚度搵？<br />\n當係異世界作品睇條氣即刻順晒<br />\n只能夠講這些機會唔屬於世上任何一條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真係好睇 高度推薦<br />\n唔好睇可以打柒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7499e3f4a946da7aab9537effef5efa108ea2dfb","tid":589480,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:33:29.000Z","msg":"即刻駁嘴"},{"pid":"07edfdc36519b7842b0d3c1e5d510998e0324399","tid":589480,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7499e3f4a946da7aab9537effef5efa108ea2dfb","tid":589480,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:33:29.000Z","msg":"即刻駁嘴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:04:08.000Z","msg":"點解要咁做"},{"pid":"ffc6493a5bbe3f3fe861f3e6e0d743a88246aac8","tid":589480,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/101704_b73252001123581c24428485a52a0f67.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F101704_b73252001123581c24428485a52a0f67.png&h=4b08ca86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937ac6de99af830e9d02b8834815f06455124c2f","tid":589480,"uid":68641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmo